README.md To Make Iraq Transition From Using Paper To Using Modern Technology About The Project 

This project aims to help Iraq transition from traditional paper-based systems to modern digital technology solutions, especially in the education and administrative sectors.

The project focuses on:

Educational management systems Digital student and school services Electronic exams and records Administrative automation Reducing paper dependency Supporting digital transformation in Iraq Author 

Developed by Hadeel Ali

